				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/realityman\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6b073d3dc9a0d88e530dec54c9d45ce2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6b073d3dc9a0d88e530dec54c9d45ce2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/realityman\" class=\"reviewer-name\">realityman</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">octubre 10, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">works nice</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ads very disappointing...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hcooh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e04bdfd6fff8a6f3c934fd095d18e065?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e04bdfd6fff8a6f3c934fd095d18e065?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hcooh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hcooh</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">octubre 10, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was a happy user of this plugin with not much to complain about...\nHowever since once of the last updates, some ad banner for Yaymail started to appear... the banner you can just close it, I would tolerate that: a free plugin needs to survive.\nBut on top of that, it also adds buttons linking to install that yaymail plugin right into my woocommerce admin email settings, links that I cannot remove. And that I am sorry, I cannot accept.\nToo bad, functions are working but I will have to find something else that does not force some ads on me and modify other plugins admin area...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does what it says and more</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lourollason\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f41970605dcdf74088d0580061eba853?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f41970605dcdf74088d0580061eba853?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lourollason\" class=\"reviewer-name\">LaDeDahDah <small>(lourollason)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">octubre 9, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Love this plugin, and I\'m disappointed that I spent so long using subpar ones. I can\'t personally justify the premium cost but will suggest it to others for its simplicity and ease of use!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin and easy to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/johnbancroftincognatecom\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/be70434093f0ebe6f49b8ef4d7cc4a62?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/be70434093f0ebe6f49b8ef4d7cc4a62?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/johnbancroftincognatecom\" class=\"reviewer-name\">john.bancroft@incognate.com</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">octubre 9, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Before using this plug in finding images could take a while and it was critical to name each one. This file manager makes it so much easier to store and find all of our media files. It is easy to set up and use.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/batisteli\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c5cd9ceb32a73dbe9eed5c723d171b20?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c5cd9ceb32a73dbe9eed5c723d171b20?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/batisteli\" class=\"reviewer-name\">batisteli</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">octubre 7, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very good!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:51:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/filebird.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:8:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:61:\"https://ps.w.org/filebird/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2356362\";s:7:\"caption\";s:35:\"Carpetas de la biblioteca de medios\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:61:\"https://ps.w.org/filebird/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=2356362\";s:7:\"caption\";s:41:\"Arrastra y suelta para organizar carpetas\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:61:\"https://ps.w.org/filebird/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=2356362\";s:7:\"caption\";s: